GERRARD MANAGEMENT SERVICES LIMITED Revenue and Financial Data

   One of the largest private client asset managers in the UK, Gerrard Investment Management provides investment management services to the UK division of private bank Barclays Wealth, itself part of banking giant Barclays. In addition to investment management, the firm offers stock brokerage, pensions, tax and inheritance planning, and individual savings accounts. Specialized services are offered to those with more investable assets. Gerrard Investment Management operates throughout the UK. Barclays acquired the company in 2003.
  







